snippet.title: Colorway Antics | A sneak peek into update 1.1
snippet.description:
Keep an eye out for Colorway Antics' Update 1.1 - filled with more sizes, more stickers, and more fun with two high-energy mini-games!

Play Colorway Antics now on Steam and Meta Quest App Lab!
